headline: KeyBank Foundation Donates $50,000 to McMahon Ryan Child Advocacy Center
summary: Funds will support efforts to prevent and intervene in child abuse as well as advocate for victims NORTHAMPTON, MA / ACCESSWIRE / December 23, 2024 / The KeyBank Foundation is donating $50,000 to support the McMahon Ryan Child Advocacy Center's efforts ...
